=========================================================
32. WHY ATOMIC?
=========================================================

Avoid race conditions for simple operations.

Faster than mutex.

=========================================================
33. ATOMIC VS MUTEX
=========================================================

Atomic:
- Simple operations
- Faster

Mutex:
- Complex operations
- Multiple variables

=========================================================
34. THREAD LOCAL STORAGE
=========================================================

thread_local int value = 0;

Each thread gets separate copy.

=========================================================
35. ASYNC
=========================================================

